<section id="Grid">

<div class="feeditem mix update">
  <div class="grid_7 ball" style="margin-left:11px">
    <p>
      <h1>Hippo Lvl. 1 Complete</h1>
      I have completed the first phase of the project, and I've now begun stage two! First on the agenda is video games, music and other neglected projects and activities. Then I'll actually get back to work and develop the full social network - packed with neat features such as customizable artist pages (like this one), personal e-stores, and, of course, social features like following, liking, sharing, commenting, etc. Stay tuned by subscribing to the Hippo Newsletter on the home page!
      <br><br>
      <span style="font-size:14px;">
        <i class="icon-time" style="margin-right:5px;opacity:.5;"></i> Sep 2, 2013
        <i class="icon-map-marker" style="margin:0 5px 0 20px;opacity:.5;"></i> Joplin, MO
        <i class="icon-tag" style="margin:0 5px 0 20px;opacity:.5;"></i> #update
      </span>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="feeditem mix photography film">
  <div class="grid_7 ball" style="margin-left:11px">
    <%= image_tag "main/photography/CaptureTheFlag/1.jpg", class: "feat"%>
    <p>
      <h1>Capture The Flag w/HitRECord</h1>
      I attended and participated in a shoot for one of the upcoming episodes of <span style="font-weight:400">HitRECord on TV</span> in Los Angeles on August 3rd. <a href="http://www.hitrecord.org" target="_blank">HitRECord</a> is an open-collaborative production company (and soon-to-be TV show) lead by Joseph Gordon-Levitt. 
      <br><br>
      HitRECord joined forces with <a href="http://pivottv.com" target="_blank">Pivot TV</a> - the brand-spanking-new, Millenial-minded television network from the good people at Participant Media (who have made a lot of great films in the name of subtle social change, including <i>The Help</i>). So when you're watching the show, look out for the episode theme regarding "Games" (:
      <br><br>
      <span style="font-size:14px;">
        <i class="icon-time" style="margin-right:5px;opacity:.5;"></i> Aug 26, 2013
        <i class="icon-map-marker" style="margin:0 5px 0 20px;opacity:.5;"></i> Los Angeles, CA
        <i class="icon-tag" style="margin:0 5px 0 20px;opacity:.5;"></i> #photography, #film
      </span>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="feeditem mix travel photography">
  <div class="grid_7 ball" style="margin-left:11px">
    <%= image_tag "main/photography/WineCountry/1.jpg", class: "feat"%>
    <p>
      <h1>Aunt's House</h1>
      My 13-or-so day family adventure was successful (July 28 - August 10, 2013). This photo was taken via turkey POV outside my aunt's house in Sutter Creek, CA. She added on that beautiful deck after buying the house a couple of years ago. I enjoyed many a mornings drinking coffee and lounging on her furniture.
